    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 28-31.</p><p>Level 24</p><p>Effortless Resistance</p><p>Beginning at 24th level, the first time you use your Legendary Resistance feature in between long rests, you do not expend a Legendary Point. Additionally, you can use the Legendary Resistance feature any number of times in a round, as long as you have the Legendary Points to fuel them.</p><p>Improved Devastating Strike</p><p>When you reach 24th level, your Devastating Strike damage calculation is increased to 8d12 x 5, or 10d12 x 5 on a critical hit.</p></div>",
